# Local LLM

**Note:** This project is a work in progress.

This repository provides tools and resources for running Large Language Models (LLMs) locally as a chatbot, with integrated Speech-to-Text (STT) and Text-to-Speech (TTS) capabilities. It enables private, offline conversational AI on your own machine.

## Features

- Run LLMs on your local machine
- Speech-to-Text (STT) and Text-to-Speech (TTS) support
- Easy setup and configuration
- Supports multiple model architectures

